moves.name: Seed Bomb
moves.description: The user slams a barrage of hard-shelled seeds down on the target from above.

moves.name: Barrage
moves.description: Round objects are hurled at the target to strike two to five times in a row.

moves.name: Hypnosis
moves.description: The user employs hypnotic suggestion to make the target fall into a deep sleep.

moves.name: Confusion
moves.description: The target is hit by a weak telekinetic force. It may also leave the target confused.

moves.name: Stomp
moves.description: The target is stomped with a big foot. It may also make the target flinch.

moves.name: Psyshock
moves.description: The user materializes an odd psychic wave to attack the target. This attack does physical damage.

moves.name: Egg Bomb
moves.description: A large egg is hurled at the target with maximum force to inflict damage.

moves.name: Wood Hammer
moves.description: The user slams its rugged body into the target to attack. The user also sustains serious damage.

moves.name: Leaf Storm
moves.description: The user whips up a storm of leaves around the target. The attack's recoil harshly reduces the user's Sp. Atk stat.
